# img — Demo GIF
# Run from public/: vhs docs/demo/img-demo.tape
# Output: docs/assets/demo.gif

Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 960
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set LoopOffset 0%

Hide
Type "bash docs/demo/img-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Sleep 32s
